resisted before it sticks.  Expect to have to focus tank him.  Make sure you get someone who knows Mistmoore well to lead group into castle or you may have train / CR to deal with.<br>
<br>
Lord Ghiosk spawns randomly upon death of black reaver.  My suggestion would be to put together a good old-fashioned CoM raid.  You will get books and also make a ranger or druid happy if their epic piece drops.  Again be sure to have enough tanks and healers since reavers are also highly MR.<br>
<br>
Getting to High Scale Kirn was harder for me than obtaining tear from Fear after it was nerfed.  Many a Hole raid stops short of the tower because they just don't have enough of specific classes to handle multiple unmezzable mobs and end up getting wiped out or evacing.  You have to move people through dungeon fast enough to avoid respawns but not so fast that everyone is OOM.  LDs and AFKs can become major problems.  Strategy is important and once again having someone experienced leading raid can make difference between success and failure.  I would recommend waiting til you are at least 50 to do this part.  Remember to kill Kurn's pet or Kirn won't spawn for shaman after you.<br>
